				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://spectrevision.net/tag/privacy/" rel="tag">privacy</a>, <a href="http://spectrevision.net/tag/statecraft/" rel="tag">state craft</a>, <a href="http://spectrevision.net/tag/tech/" rel="tag">tech</a>			</span>
						
