                        <li class="tweet">
                            <p><a href="https://t.co/M8exmtQ4OF">spectrevision</a> Symmetrical and not so much <a target="_blank" href=http://t.co/BIwKAy0LpY>http://t.co/BIwKAy0LpY</a>  Why are we symmetrical on the outside, but not on the inside?</p>
                            <p class="tweet_meta">
                                <span><a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/spectrevision/status/490953890863403009">3 days</a></span>
